==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Desultoriness
<hw>Des"ul*to*ri*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality of being
desultory or without order or method; unconnectedness.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The seeming <qex>desultoriness</qex> of my method.</q>
<rj><qau>Boyle.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Desultorious</ent>⟦br⟧
